CATEGORY :
Create :    POST http://localhost:8090/api/v2/ecommerce/category/add-category
            {
                "categoryName": "snacks",
                "description": "packed munch-ons"
            }

Retrieve -  all GET http://localhost:8090/api/v2/ecommerce/category/all
            by name GET http://localhost:8090/api/v2/ecommerce/category/get-category-name/snacks
            by description GET http://localhost:8090/api/v2/ecommerce/category/get-category-description/clothes

Update -    by name PUT http://localhost:8090/api/v2/ecommerce/category/update-category-name/fashion
            {
                "description": "apparels"
            }

            by description PUT http://localhost:8090/api/v2/ecommerce/category/update-category-description/packed%20munch-ons
            {
                "categoryName": "nibbles"
            }

Delete :    DELETE http://localhost:8090/api/v2/ecommerce/category/delete-category/4

